Lady Hawk awoke once again, finally fully rested from her long walk 
through the desert. "Now lets see what I can do." she stepped up to 
her console and programmed the results from her last test. she stared 
at the results, playing with them for a while. the translife rat DNA 
didn't have the qualities that the bug had, the bug was natural where 
the rat was Artificial intelligence.

she opened another sample, this one had the scorpion DNA, she 
combined a drop of that with a drop of cobra DNA. the results came 
almost immediately. the chemicals in the poison were undeniably 
potent, not to mention the diagram showed potential for a poison 
sting and a poison bite. She quickly stored the results in a side 
program incrypted only to her. If she could avoid giving this 
information to Zardus she would. 

Next she decided to put two natural enemies together. another drop of 
cobra DNA and a drop of Mongoose DNA. the results took longer this 
time.
